    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279730/extras/ee4866872c82dc133d7b0b4347ab094a.poster.avif?t=1745398879\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279730/extras/ee4866872c82dc133d7b0b4347ab094a.webm?t=1745398879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279730/extras/ee4866872c82dc133d7b0b4347ab094a.mp4?t=1745398879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>投身于反复的战争与势力间的纠葛</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战火正在卡米洛特全境蔓延。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>请成为掌握圣剑之力的君主，捍卫领地，严惩破坏和平的异教徒国家</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>准备好通过战略性操作引领战争走向胜利了吗？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279730/extras/dd4d6ce30221f885e1d91f6c8af98add.poster.avif?t=1745398879\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279730/extras/dd4d6ce30221f885e1d91f6c8af98add.webm?t=1745398879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279730/extras/dd4d6ce30221f885e1d91f6c8af98add.mp4?t=1745398879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>▶加强游戏沉浸感的故事</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>为胜利所做的黑暗交易。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> 使用圣剑之力要付出什么代价？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> 卡米洛特王国能否取得胜利？只有你能找到这些问题的答案。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279730/extras/f5f03d260bfb5dbfeb2816e3a6254ee1.poster.avif?t=1745398879\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279730/extras/f5f03d260bfb5dbfeb2816e3a6254ee1.webm?t=1745398879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279730/extras/f5f03d260bfb5dbfeb2816e3a6254ee1.mp4?t=1745398879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>▶与传说中的英雄军团展开激烈战斗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收集亚瑟王传说中的英雄们，培养强大的军团。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> 按情况交替使用获得的各种遗物，在实战中检验策略。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279730/extras/64ab3b20ddd448936fa22da4218ae56b.poster.avif?t=1745398879\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279730/extras/64ab3b20ddd448936fa22da4218ae56b.webm?t=1745398879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279730/extras/64ab3b20ddd448936fa22da4218ae56b.mp4?t=1745398879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>▶体验回合制策略战斗的战争</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>由玩家自行布局的战斗，以及为此提供支撑的英雄设计。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> 《亚瑟王：传说崛起》展现了回合制战略游戏的进化。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> 今后还会添加更多故事章节、游戏模式和新的玩法，敬请期待！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279730/extras/4633f4ffa9135fbbfb6f7d7baac56d89.poster.avif?t=1745398879\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279730/extras/4633f4ffa9135fbbfb6f7d7baac56d89.webm?t=1745398879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279730/extras/4633f4ffa9135fbbfb6f7d7baac56d89.mp4?t=1745398879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
